name: The Black Garden: Where am I?
description: @EndemicJa | The gardener wakes to find that they are no longer in a quaint suburban yard. Have they been transported here … has the world transfigured around them? The surrounding space is engulfed by greenery; Massive leaves, sinewy stalks, winding vines everywhere. the gardener turns their gaze skywards and they are met by a bright light, but … before that? … a large hand …
